# CODEOWNERS
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic PR reviewer assignment.
# Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
#
# Order is important; the last matching pattern takes precedence.
# Owners can be GitHub usernames, email addresses, or team names.
#
# Examples:
#   /app/**/*.tsx @frontend-team
#   /lib/db/** @database-team
#   *.md @docs-team

# Default owner for everything in the repo
# This is a good practice to ensure all PRs get reviewed
* @pawelc

